Sentencas: La1-xSrxTi0.80Fe0.20O3;{0.10 <= x <= 0.40} perovskite ceramics material has been prepared by solid-state route technique.

Sentencas: The samples, prepared as pellets, underwent characterization through X-ray diffraction and scanning electron microscope for structural study, by thermo gravimetric analyser for thermal study, and by impedance spectrometer for dielectric and conductive study.
